 </span>
                <br />
Tarih: 31.08.2012   Saat:19.00
                <br />
        <br />
        <img src="images/yazilar_img/kasim2012/se_bariseylemi.jpg"  alt="Fethiye Davası" style="clear: left; display: block;
            float: left; visibility: visible; position: static; width: 450px; height: 330px;" /><br />
 
